m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m In conclusion, FastAPI offers several advantages over Flask, including high performance, strong typing,         \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m automatic API documentation, and robust error handling. By following best practices and using tools like Redis  \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m caching, we can build scalable and maintainable APIs that meet the demands of modern applications.              \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m╰─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\n"],"text/html":["<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">╭─────────────────────────────────────────────────── AI REVIEW ───────────────────────────────────────────────────╮</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                  <span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline\">Introduction to FastAPI and Flask Comparison</span>                                   <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> As a seasoned AI Software Architect, I'll provide an in-depth analysis of why FastAPI is better than Flask for  <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> our project requirements. We'll also review some code examples, discuss potential issues, and suggest           <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> improvements for production-ready applications.                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #800080; text-decoration-color: #800080; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline\">Why FastAPI?</span>                                                                                                    <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> FastAPI is a modern, fast (high-performance), web framework for building APIs with Python 3.7+ based on         <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> standard Python type hints. Here are some key reasons why FastAPI stands out:                                   <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> • Speed</span>: FastAPI is significantly faster than Flask, thanks to its asynchronous architecture and support for   <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span>ASGI (Asynchronous Server Gateway Interface).                                                                <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> • Strongly Typed</span>: FastAPI is built on top of Python type hints, which provides better code completion, reduces <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span>runtime errors, and improves overall code quality.                                                           <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> • Automatic API Documentation</span>: FastAPI automatically generates interactive API documentation using Swagger UI  <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span>and Redoc, making it easier to test and document APIs.                                                       <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> • Robust Error Handling</span>: FastAPI provides built-in support for error handling, including automatic error       <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span>handling for unhandled exceptions and support for custom error handlers.                                     <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #800080; text-decoration-color: #800080; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline\">Code Review: FastAPI vs. Flask</span>                                                                                  <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> Let's compare a simple \"Hello, World!\" API example using both FastAPI and Flask:                                <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #800080; text-decoration-color: #800080; font-weight: bold\">FastAPI Example</span>                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">from</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> fastapi </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">import</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> FastAPI</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                   </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">app </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">=</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> FastAPI()</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #a6e22e; text-decoration-color: #a6e22e; background-color: #272822\">@app</span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">.</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">get(</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"/\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">)</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                 </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #66d9ef; text-decoration-color: #66d9ef; background-color: #272822\">def</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #a6e22e; text-decoration-color: #a6e22e; background-color: #272822\">read_root</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">():</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                              </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    </span><span style=\"color: #66d9ef; text-decoration-color: #66d9ef; background-color: #272822\">return</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> {</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"Hello\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"World\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">}</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                 </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #800080; text-decoration-color: #800080; font-weight: bold\">Flask Example</span>                                                                                                   <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">from</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> flask </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">import</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> Flask, jsonify</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                              </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">app </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">=</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> Flask(__name__)</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                         </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #a6e22e; text-decoration-color: #a6e22e; background-color: #272822\">@app</span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">.</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">route(</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"/\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">, methods</span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">=</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">[</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"GET\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">])</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                              </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #66d9ef; text-decoration-color: #66d9ef; background-color: #272822\">def</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #a6e22e; text-decoration-color: #a6e22e; background-color: #272822\">read_root</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">():</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                              </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    </span><span style=\"color: #66d9ef; text-decoration-color: #66d9ef; background-color: #272822\">return</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> jsonify({</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"Hello\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"World\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">})</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                        </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> Both examples achieve the same result, but the FastAPI version is more concise and takes advantage of Python    <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> type hints.                                                                                                     <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #800080; text-decoration-color: #800080; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline\">Issues and Improvements</span>                                                                                         <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> To further improve our FastAPI application, let's address some potential issues:                                <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> • Error Handling</span>: While FastAPI provides robust error handling, we should still implement custom error         <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span>handlers to handle specific error scenarios. For example:                                                    <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                            </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                            </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">   </span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                            </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> from fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException                                                                      <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> app = FastAPI()                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> @app.get(\"/\") def read_root(): try: # Code that might raise an exception return {\"Hello\": \"World\"} except       <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> Exception as e: raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=str(e))                                             <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">*   **Redis Caching**: To improve performance, we can integrate Redis caching for heavy APIs. We'll use the </span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">  </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">`aioredis` library to interact with Redis asynchronously:</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                     </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    ```python</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                 </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">import aioredis</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">from fastapi import FastAPI</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                   </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">app = FastAPI()</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">redis = aioredis.from_url(\"redis://localhost\")</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">@app.get(\"/\")</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                 </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">async def read_root():</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                        </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    cached_value = await redis.get(\"hello_world\")</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                             </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    if cached_value:</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                          </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        return {\"Hello\": cached_value}</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                        </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    else:</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                     </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        # Compute the value and cache it</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                      </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        value = {\"Hello\": \"World\"}</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                            </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        await redis.set(\"hello_world\", value)</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                 </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        return value</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                          </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> • Production Suggestions</span>:                                                                                      <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">    • </span>Use a WSGI server like <span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080; background-color: #000000; font-weight: bold\">uvicorn</span> or <span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080; background-color: #000000; font-weight: bold\">gunicorn</span> to run your FastAPI application in production.                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">    • </span>Implement logging and monitoring to track application performance and errors.                             <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">    • </span>Use a load balancer to distribute traffic across multiple instances of your application.                  <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"font-weight: bold\">    • </span>Consider using a containerization platform like Docker to simplify deployment and management.             <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> By following these guidelines and best practices, we can build high-performance, scalable, and maintainable     <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> APIs using FastAPI.                                                                                             <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #800080; text-decoration-color: #800080; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline\">Example Use Case:</span>                                                                                               <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> Here's an example of a more complex API that demonstrates the use of FastAPI, Redis caching, and error          <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> handling:                                                                                                       <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">from</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> fastapi </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">import</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> FastAPI, HTTPException</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                    </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">import</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> aioredis</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">app </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">=</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> FastAPI()</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">redis </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">=</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> aioredis</span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">.</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">from_url(</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"redis://localhost\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">)</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span styl