t-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">total,</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"available\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: memory</span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">.</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">available,</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                        </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"used\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: memory</span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">.</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">used,</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                  </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text