t-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        </span><span style=\"color: #66d9ef; text-decoration-color: #66d9ef; background-color: #272822\">return</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> {</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"error\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"Failed to retrieve memory information\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">}</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                             </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    </span><span style=\"color: #66d9ef; text-decoration-color: #66d9ef; background-color: #272822\">return</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> {</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                  </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"total\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: memory_info[</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"total\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">] </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">/</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #ae81ff; text-decoration-color: #ae81ff; background-color: #272822\">1024</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">*</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ae81ff; text-decoration-color: #ae81ff; background-color: #272822\">1024</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">),</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                        </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"available\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: memory_info[</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"available\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">] </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">/</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #ae81ff; text-decoration-color: #ae81ff; background-color: #272822\">1024</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">*</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ae81ff; text-decoration-color: #ae81ff; background-color: #272822\">1024</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">),</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"used\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: memory_info[</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"used\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">] </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">/</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #ae81ff; text-decoration-color: #ae81ff; background-color: #272822\">1024</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ff4689; text-decoration-color: #ff4689; background-color: #272822\">*</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #ae81ff; text-decoration-color: #ae81ff; background-color: #272822\">1024</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">),</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                          </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">        </span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"percentage\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">: memory_info[</span><span style=\"color: #e6db74; text-decoration-color: #e6db74; background-color: #272822\">\"percentage\"</span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">]</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\"> </span><span style=\"color: #f8f8f2; text-decoration-color: #f8f8f2; background-color: #272822\">    }</span><span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                         </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> <span style=\"background-color: #272822\">                                                                                                               </span> <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>                                                                                                                 <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> This updated version uses FastAPI to create an async endpoint, separates concerns, and implements error         <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span> handling and logging.                                                                                           <span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #808000; text-decoration-color: #808000\">╰─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯</span>\n","</pre>\n"]},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","output_type":"stream","text":["\n","You: remember: Use Redis caching for heavy APIs\n"]},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["\u001b[32m╭──────────────────────────────────╮\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;32mMEMORY SAVED\u001b[0m                     \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m                                  \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m Use Redis caching for heavy APIs \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[32m╰──────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\n"],"text/html":["<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">╭──────────────────────────────────╮</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000; font-weight: bold\">MEMORY SAVED</span>                     <span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">│</span>                                  <span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">│</span> Use Redis caching for heavy APIs <span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">╰──────────────────────────────────╯</span>\n","</pre>\n"]},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","output_type":"stream","text":["\n","You: What is our backend framework?\n"]},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["\n"],"text/html":["<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\">\n","</pre>\n"]},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["\u001b[36m╭──────────────────────────────╮\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mPROVA AI V3\u001b[0m                  \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32mAI Coding Architect Response\u001b[0m \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[36m╰──────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\n"],"text/html":["<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080\">╭──────────────────────────────╮</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080; font-weight: bold\">PROVA AI V3</span>                  <span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080\">│</span> <span style=\"color: #008000; text-decoration-color: #008000\">AI Coding Architect Response</span> <span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080\">│</span>\n","<span style=\"color: #008080; text-decoration-color: #008080\">╰──────────────────────────────╯</span>\n","</pre>\n"]},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":["\u001b[33m╭─\u001b[0m\u001b[33m──────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[33m \u001b[0m\u001b[33mAI REVIEW\u001b[0m\u001b[33m \u001b[0m\u001b[33m──────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[33m─╮\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mBackend Framework Confirmation\u001b[0m Our backend framework is indeed \u001b[1mFastAPI\u001b[0m, as per the project requirements. This   \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m framework is well-suited for building high-performance, scalable, and robust APIs.                              \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCode Review\u001b[0m Since we haven't written any code yet, there's nothing to review. However, I can provide a basic    \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m example of a FastAPI application to get us started:                                                             \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                                               \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;255;70;137;48;2;39;40;34mfrom\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34mfastapi\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;255;70;137;48;2;39;40;34mimport\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34mFastAPI\u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                  \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34mapp\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;255;70;137;48;2;39;40;34m=\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34mFastAPI\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m(\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m)\u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                              \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;166;226;46;48;2;39;40;34m@app\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;255;70;137;48;2;39;40;34m.\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34mget\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m(\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34m\"\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34m/\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34m\"\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m)\u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                                \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;102;217;239;48;2;39;40;34mdef\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;166;226;46;48;2;39;40;34mread_root\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m(\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m)\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m:\u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                             \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m    \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;102;217;239;48;2;39;40;34mreturn\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m{\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34m\"\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34mmessage\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34m\"\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m:\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34m\"\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34mWelcome to our FastAPI application\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;230;219;116;48;2;39;40;34m\"\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;248;248;242;48;2;39;40;34m}\u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                 \u001b[0m\u001b[48;2;39;40;34m \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[48;2;39;40;34m                                                                                                               \u001b[0m \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mIssues\u001b[0m None identified at this point, as we're just starting to build our application.                          \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mImprovements\u001b[0m To further improve our application, we can consider the following:                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36m 1 \u001b[0m\u001b[1mAPI Documentation\u001b[0m: We can use tools like Swagger or Redoc to generate API documentation automatically.       \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36m 2 \u001b[0m\u001b[1mError Handling\u001b[0m: Implement robust error handling mechanisms to handle unexpected errors and exceptions.       \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36m 3 \u001b[0m\u001b[1mSecurity\u001b[0m: Integrate security features like authentication and authorization to protect our API.              \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mProduction Suggestions\u001b[0m For production, we'll be using \u001b[1mPostgreSQL\u001b[0m as our database, as per the project            \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m requirements. To ensure a smooth production deployment, we can consider the following:                          \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                                 \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b[33m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36m 1 \u001b[0m\u001b[1mContainerization\u001b[0m: Use Docker to containerize our application and ensure consistency across different         \u001b[33m│\u001b[0m\n","\u001b